name: MyOfficeProducts
overview: MyOfficeProducts, Inc. offers office supplies, office furniture, computer and information technology supplies, and coffee and break room supplies in the United States. It offers office supplies, including binders and accessories, boards and easels, business/travel bags and accessories, calendars and planners, cash handling products, desk organizers, envelopes and forms, filing supplies, general supplies, healthcare supplies, labels and labeling systems, mailing and shipping, paper and pads, storage and organizers, teaching and art products, tools and equipment, and writing and correction products. The company also provides furniture, including armoires and bookcases; carts and stands; chairs, chair mats, and accessories; filings, storage products, and accessories; furniture accessories; furniture collections, desks, and tables; office decor and lighting products; and panel systems and accessories. In addition, it offers technology products, including audio and video players, cameras and scanners, computer accessories, displays and digital projectors, drives and medias, multimedia players, networking and cables products, office machines and electronics, peripherals and memory devices, power and backup devices, radio and mobile technology products, shredders and accessories, surveillance and security devices, and telephone and communication products, as well as printers, multifunction, and printing supplies. The company offers its products online, as well as through warehouse distribution centers. MyOfficeProducts, Inc., was formerly known as Partners In Business, Inc., and is based in Franklin, Tennessee. As of November 8, 2010, MyOfficeProducts, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of HiTouch Business Services.
